$ ahnentafel 1010b
base-10 value: 10
family relation: father's mother's father
generations back: 3

$ ahnentafel 31
ahnentafel number in binary: 11111
family relation: mother's mother's mother's mother
generations back: 4

$ ahnentafel mother\'s father\'s father
ahnentafel number in binary: 1100
ahnentafel number in base-10: 12
generations back: 3

# notice that in the last example the ' had to be escaped since
# the shell treats the single-quote as a special character